# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# TechPulse AI — Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Gemini API (REQUIRED) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get a free key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# The platform will NOT start content generation without this.
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Primary model (first choice). Others are used as fallback automatically.
# Available free models: gemini-2.5-flash | gemini-2.0-flash | gemini-2.0-flash-lite | gemini-2.5-pro
GEMINI_PRIMARY_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash

# ── Admin Dashboard ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ADMIN_USERNAME=admin
ADMIN_PASSWORD=admin123
JWT_SECRET=dev-secret-change-me

# ── Scheduler ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Enable/disable the autonomous content generation scheduler
SCHEDULER_ENABLED=true
# How often to generate content (milliseconds)
# 3600000 = 1 hour | 1800000 = 30 min | 7200000 = 2 hours
SCHEDULER_INTERVAL_MS=3600000

# ── Agent Pipeline Tuning ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Quality gate threshold (0-100). Articles scoring below this are rejected.
QUALITY_GATE_THRESHOLD=60
# Max articles generated per scheduler cycle
MAX_ARTICLES_PER_CYCLE=2
# Delay between article generations in ms (respects Gemini RPM limits)
INTER_ARTICLE_DELAY_MS=15000

# ── Site Identity ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_NAME=TechPulse AI
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_TAGLINE=Autonomous AI Journalism for the Tech World

# ── Logging ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DEBUG = show all | INFO = standard | WARN = warnings+errors | ERROR = errors only
LOG_LEVEL=info
